** Refractor checklist **
- strings.dart to store every hard coded string
- wrapper for safeArea and padding
- style constants 
    - padding
    - font
    - colors
    - decorations
    - height and width
    - sizedBox as verticalSpace, horizontalSpace

--------
** Commit Format **

[Emoji] [Type] [Message]

Emoji to indicate the domain of work - ui(🖌️), logic(⚙️), test(🧪)
Type - Add, Remove, Update, Fix, Rework, Polish
Message - anything to the context

Eg. 🖌️ Polish onboarding screen

